headline: Down 69%, Nike Is a Brilliant Stock to Buy Only if You Believe 1 Thing
summary: Nike (NYSE: NKE) needs no introduction.  Nike's winning culture has been replaced by a losing track record due to ongoing challenges.  If you're taking a closer look at Nike stock, know that adding the company to your portfolio is only a brilliant move if you believe one thing.
